1/ to clear previous run files:

	sh clear.sh

      NOTE- This will delete ALL .txt files.


2/ to invoke router,host,controller:

	python host.py 0 0 sender 40 5 &

	python host.py 1 2 receiver &

	python router.py 0 0 1 &

	python router.py 1 1 2 &

	python controller.py host 0 1 router 0 1 lan 0 1 2&



